metadata.name: Aefin
metadata.description:
Repressing negative feelings does a lot of damage, it is best to accept that they are there and channel them into positive actions. Expectral is a collection that seeks to manifest all the negativity of our bodies and minds in order to accept it and move on. Knowing our demons, accepting that they exist and working on them every day is a path to true change.

Expectral is a collection of 25 NFTs PFPs made 1/1. Having an exclusive avatar, where all are rarities is the goal of this collection.

3000x3000 px  / 300 ppi
